    {
      "id": "sybil_1_listing_1",
      "firm_id": "sybil_1",
      "description": "Hey there! Thanks for stopping by. It honestly breaks my heart a little to let this beauty go, but it's time for someone else to enjoy the ride. I\u2019ve treated this car like a member of the family\u2014always garaged, hand-washed every Sunday, and kept in absolutely stunning, showroom-ready shape. You\u2019d be hard-pressed to find a single blemish on her; she looks and drives just like the day she rolled off the lot. If you're looking for a ride that's been loved and meticulously cared for, you've found it. Let's get you behind the wheel for a test drive!",
