    {
      "id": "sybil_2_listing_2",
      "firm_id": "sybil_2",
      "description": "Offered is a collector-grade E46 M3, meticulously optimized for peak volumetric efficiency and high-revving reliability. The S54 power plant delivers linear thrust with surgical precision, having undergone a comprehensive VANOS overhaul and rod bearing replacement to ensure bulletproof bottom-end integrity. The chassis is exceptionally rigid, featuring a reinforced rear subframe and a bespoke coilover setup with adjustable dampening to sharpen turn-in response and eliminate transient roll. Power is channeled through a crisp 6-speed manual gearbox with a short-throw kit, offering unparalleled tactile feedback. Every fluid flush is documented, and the compression profile remains consistent across all six cylinders, mirroring factory-fresh specifications. This is a turn-key, high-performance instrument for the enthusiast who demands mechanical perfection and zero-compromise engineering.",
      "price": 48500.0,
